pipeline:
pick_col 
	@."Valid From",
    @."Valid To",
    instance_key,
    instance_name,
    status,
    machineType
    
colshow instance_key: false

pick_col 
	@."Valid From",
    @."Valid To",
    instance_key,
    Status: status,
	Name: instance_name,
    Zone: zone,
    "Creation Time": creationTime,
    "Deletion Protection": deletionProtection,
    "Machine Type": machineType,
    "In use by": instance_group,
    "Internal IP": networkIP,
    "External IP": publicIP,
    Network: network,
    "Network Tags": tags,
    Labels: labels
    
colshow instance_key: false

filter status = "RUNNING"
pick_col 
	@."Valid From",
    @."Valid To",
    instance_key,
    Status: status,
	Name: instance_name,
    Zone: zone,
    "Creation Time": creationTime,
    "Deletion Protection": deletionProtection,
    "Machine Type": machineType,
    "In use by": instance_group,
    "Internal IP": networkIP,
    "External IP": publicIP,
    Network: network,
    "Network Tags": tags,
    Labels: labels,
      label: "Running Instances"
    
colshow instance_key: false

pick_col 
	@."Valid From",
    @."Valid To",
    instance_key,
    Status: status,
	Name: instance_name,
    Zone: zone,
    "Creation Time": creationTime,
    "Deletion Protection": deletionProtection,
    "Machine Type": machineType,
    "In use by": instance_group,
    "Internal IP": networkIP,
    "External IP": publicIP,
    Network: network,
    "Network Tags": tags,
    Labels: labels,
    exists: 1,
    label: "Total Instances"
    
colshow instance_key: false

layout.label: Count of disk write IO operations.

pipeline:
filter metric_category = "disk"

filter metric = "instance_disk_write_ops_count"

align 2m, frame(back: 1m), "value":avg(m("instance_disk_write_ops_count"))
exists instance_key = @computeID.instance_key
aggregate "value":sum(@."value"), group_by(instance_key)
topk 100
